The magical pumpkin is a reward for the 2020 Halloween event. The item is used to plant a pumpkin in a garden or formal garden of a player-owned house using a watering can. Interacting with the magical pumpkin causes the player to take and eat pieces of different coloured candy. After eating the candy, the player will say Ooh piece of candy.. The candy does not provide any boosts, nor does it heal any missing health.

If lost, or if not received due to completing the halloween event as free-to-play, the magical pumpkin can be reclaimed from Diango.

This item can be stored in the toy box of a costume room.

A magical pumpkin displayed in a formal garden of a player-owned house.

The '''magical pumpkin''' is a reward for the [[2020 Halloween event]]. The item is used to plant a [[Pumpkin (Construction)|pumpkin]] in a [[garden]] or [[formal garden]] of a [[player-owned house]] using a [[watering can]]. Interacting with the magical pumpkin causes the player to take and eat pieces of different [[Candy (pumpkin)|coloured candy]]. After eating the candy, the player will say {{RSChat|Ooh piece of candy.}}. The candy does not provide any boosts, nor does it heal any missing health.

If lost, or if not received due to completing the halloween event as free-to-play, the magical pumpkin can be reclaimed from [[Diango]].

{{Costume storage|toy box}}
